parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the torque converter can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle may suddenly lose power or acceleration
the transmission may slip or hesitate
the vehicle may not shift into gear
or the vehicle may become stuck in neutral.

symptoms: The vehicle may suddenly lose power or acceleration

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the gear shifter can cause the vehicle to become stuck in park or fail to shift into gear, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The gear shifter may become stuck in park
the vehicle may not shift into gear
or the brake lights may remain illuminated even after the vehicle is turned off.
